staircase_newbee18647@newbee.name: staircase_newbee18647
staircase_newbee18647@newbee.examine: They are constructed of smooth, beautiful marble.

floor_newbee18646@newbee.name: floor_newbee18646
floor_newbee18646@newbee.examine: It appears to be the crest of the Harlequin Guild.

fountain@newbee.name: fountain
fountain@newbee.desc[0]: A small icy fountain burbles gently in the centre of the room.

statue_newbee18640@newbee.name: statue_newbee18640
statue_newbee18640@newbee.examine:
Upon closer inspection you see that the statue has a small &+Gplaque&* affixed
to it.  The face looks remarkably familiar also.

obj18614@newbee.name: obj18614
obj18614@newbee.desc[0]: A finely crafted newbie mace is waiting for a worthy owner.

obj18612@newbee.name: obj18612
obj18612@newbee.desc[0]: A pair of neat looking leggings are here.

obj18604@newbee.name: obj18604
obj18604@newbee.desc[0]: A dark newbie cloak is lying here hoping to smother you.

obj18610@newbee.name: obj18610
obj18610@newbee.desc[0]: The horns of the great Minotaur lie here.

wall_newbee18639@newbee.name: wall_newbee18639
wall_newbee18639@newbee.examine:
There is a crude picture of a man with the head of a bull with some &+Gwriting
next to it.

obj18607@newbee.name: obj18607
obj18607@newbee.desc[0]: Someone's pet dragon has escaped and left his collar here.

obj18602_2@newbee.name: obj18602_2
obj18602_2@newbee.desc[0]: A bright green newbie vest is lying here looking for a body to hug.

obj18602_1@newbee.name: obj18602_1
obj18602_1@newbee.desc[0]: A bright green newbie vest is lying here looking for a body to hug.

obj18601@newbee.name: obj18601
obj18601@newbee.desc[0]: A shiny newbie sword is lying here waiting to be possessed.

plaque_newbee18640@newbee.name: plaque_newbee18640
plaque_newbee18640@newbee.examine:
It says:

Maynard, Death Jester of the Harlequins.

obj18613@newbee.name: obj18613
obj18613@newbee.desc[0]: A set of nifty sleeves is here.

grate_newbee18605@newbee.name: grate_newbee18605
grate_newbee18605@newbee.examine: A ladder leads down into darkness.

door_newbee18646@newbee.name: door_newbee18646
door_newbee18646@newbee.examine: A brighter hallway leads off that way.

door_newbee18602@newbee.name: door_newbee18602
door_newbee18602@newbee.examine: More of the hallway there... how exciting!

floor_newbee18644@newbee.name: floor_newbee18644
floor_newbee18644@newbee.examine: It appears to be the Crest of the Harlequin Guild.

obj18611@newbee.name: obj18611
obj18611@newbee.desc[0]: The hide of the great Minotaur is lying here.

staircase_newbee18642@newbee.name: staircase_newbee18642
staircase_newbee18642@newbee.examine: They are constructed of smooth, beautiful marble.

door_newbee18607@newbee.name: door_newbee18607
door_newbee18607@newbee.examine: More of the hallway there... how exciting!

door_newbee18611@newbee.name: door_newbee18611
door_newbee18611@newbee.examine: A corner in the passage lies to the west.

obj18609@newbee.name: obj18609
obj18609@newbee.desc[0]: A jar of glowing fluid wants to brighten your day.

obj18605@newbee.name: obj18605
obj18605@newbee.desc[0]: A newbie signet ring is lying in the dust here.

door_newbee18606_s@newbee.name: door_newbee18606_s
door_newbee18606_s@newbee.examine: A small room lies to the south... you hear something moving about inside.

obj18603@newbee.name: obj18603
obj18603@newbee.desc[0]: A bright newbie helm is hoping a loose head will wander by.

obj18606_1@newbee.name: obj18606_1
obj18606_1@newbee.desc[0]: A shiny newbie dagger is lying here looking for a back to stab.

portal_newbee18629@newbee.name: portal_newbee18629
portal_newbee18629@newbee.examine:
It looks as if you could go down into it... but you can't be sure of where
you will end up, or if you can get back.

sign_newbee18612@newbee.name: sign_newbee18612
sign_newbee18612@newbee.examine:
The sign next to the stairs says:

If you are below 70hps and alone, or below 40hps then bugger off!
Or else don't blame me if you die...

obj18606@newbee.name: obj18606
obj18606@newbee.desc[0]: A shiny newbie dagger is lying here looking for a back to stab.

door_newbee18612@newbee.name: door_newbee18612
door_newbee18612@newbee.examine: You peer into a cluttered little room to the east.

obj18602@newbee.name: obj18602
obj18602@newbee.desc[0]: A bright green newbie vest is lying here looking for a body to hug.

door_newbee18644_s@newbee.name: door_newbee18644_s
door_newbee18644_s@newbee.examine: A brighter hallway leads off that way.

obj18608@newbee.name: obj18608
obj18608@newbee.desc[0]: A key with the newbie crest on it is here.

writing_newbee18639@newbee.name: writing_newbee18639
writing_newbee18639@newbee.examine: The writing appears to says 'beware the Minotaur...'

grate_newbee18606@newbee.name: grate_newbee18606
grate_newbee18606@newbee.examine: You see a ladder leading up.

newbee18609@newbee.title: The End Of The Passage
newbee18609@newbee.description:
Ahhh... at last, the end of the hallway... you can exit into open
air to the west, or return to the east and make sure you didn't miss
anything.

newbee18631@newbee.title: A Passage
newbee18631@newbee.description:
Ick... this place is just disgusting.  You try and stay clear of the
walls, but the passage is so narrow you keep bumping them anyway.  You
are almost convinced that the fungus coating the walls is grabbing at
you too.

newbee18629@newbee.title: The Red Room
newbee18629@newbee.description:
It takes you a moment to realize that the red glow here is coming
from a round &+Gportal&* on the floor.  It looks almost as if someone had
painted a picture of a white icy fountain bubbling invigorating water.
Oddly enough, it is so realistic you can feel the cold air and the wet
mist coming out of the picture.

newbee18641@newbee.title: The Hallway
newbee18641@newbee.description:
As you continue wandering down the hallway, you notice banners,
pictures, and other fine decorations adorning the walls all along
this passage.  It seems very different from the dismal passage where
you entered.

newbee18603@newbee.title: A Nexus
newbee18603@newbee.description:
Well... you've reached an intersection of two passages, to the north
and east, the passage brightens, while the darker hallway continues to
the south.

newbee18608@newbee.title: An Open Field
newbee18608@newbee.description:
Finally, you are in an open field... it is so nice to breathe fresh air
again!  You can return to that dank, smelly place to the east, or take the
exit to the north which appears to lead into a large field.

newbee18600@newbee.title: The Entrance To The Newbie Zone
newbee18600@newbee.description:
Ahhh... the entrance to the newbie zone!  Just the place you have
been looking for.  Well, when you've readied yourself you can enter
to the north.

newbee18634@newbee.title: An Intersection Of Passages
newbee18634@newbee.description:
Cold, smelly, and coated with green fungus... just like last week's
left-overs.  Furthermore you want nothing to do with either, you just
want out right now.

newbee18632@newbee.title: The Entrance
newbee18632@newbee.description:
It is dark, dank, disgusting and cold up here.  Plus you here the
sounds of creatures all around you... and somehow they don't sound
friendly.  It is probably wise to exercise some degree of caution
here... no telling what you may run into here.

newbee18630@newbee.title: A Branching Passage
newbee18630@newbee.description:
The north-south passage branches to the east here.  There is a queer red
glow coming from that way as well, along with a faint breeze.

newbee18605@newbee.title: The Dark Pit
newbee18605@newbee.description:
Ick... a dark damp dirty pit.  Even worse, what is that dark damp
dirty thing looking at you from the corner?  Ewww... maybe you should
go back up where it is a bit safer, unless you think you can tackle
that thing in the corner.

newbee18604@newbee.title: A Narrow Passage
newbee18604@newbee.description:
The thin passage is plain and undecorated, but still clean.  It
ends abruptly to the south at a small oak door, behind which you here
movement...

newbee18644@newbee.title: A Bright Hallway
newbee18644@newbee.description:
Wow!  What a change from the dismal passage to the south.  Whoever
keeps this room up must really like newbies.  The walls and floor are
clean, and tastefully decorated.  You also notice an interesting design
on the &+Cfloor&*.

newbee18637@newbee.title: Yet Another Corner
newbee18637@newbee.description:
The passage turns here and heads north.  You sense something up ahead
that way, but you aren't sure what.  You aren't sure if you want to know
what either at this point.

newbee18633@newbee.title: Another Corner
newbee18633@newbee.description:
Well... what is there to say.  More fungus, more weird sounds, and a
slight breeze from the north.  Bet you want to sign a lease, don't ya...

newbee18635@newbee.title: A Turn In The Passage
newbee18635@newbee.description:
This place is just plain nauseating... it certainly smells as if
something (or someone) died in here.  You hope you aren't next, but
from the sounds you hear all around you, it seems as if something has
other ideas about that.

newbee18601@newbee.title: The Beginning Of The Passage
newbee18601@newbee.description:
You find yourself entering a long corridor.  You can hear the sound
of creatures roaming about, but you can't tell where the sound emanates
from exactly.
   Exits lead to the east along the hallway, and south back to the
entrance.

newbee18623@newbee.title: A Corner In The Hallway
newbee18623@newbee.description:
You can hear creatures moving all around you... and it is not
a comforting sound at all.  The furnishing is nothing to speak of
either, plain grey brick walls with green fungus (or something)
growing on them.

newbee18639@newbee.title: A Large Room
newbee18639@newbee.description:
As you enter, you light glints of the wall to the east.  There appears
to be words scrawled on the &+Gwall&*, and a crude picture.  To the west the
room extends beyond the reach of your light, and the dark shadows make you
paranoid... anything could be hiding there.  You are painfully aware of
how exposed you are without walls around you.

newbee18606@newbee.title: A Small Room
newbee18606@newbee.description:
Hmmm... this is an interesting little room.  Ack, and there is
an interesting little creature staring at you too.  He looks a bit
surprised at your intrusion.  You can leave via the doors north or
east, or you can stay and annoy him a bit more.  There also appears
to be some type of well down here also, but it has a rather secure
grate covering it.

newbee18620@newbee.title: A Turn In The Passage
newbee18620@newbee.description:
This corner is much like all the others... except you see a strange
glow coming from the south.  Could be an exit... you hope.

newbee18646@newbee.title: A Bright Hallway
newbee18646@newbee.description:
Wow!  What a change from the dismal passage to the west.  Whoever keeps
this  room up must really like newbies.  The walls and floor are clean, and
tastefully decorated.  You also notice an interesting design on the &+Cfloor.

newbee18626@newbee.title: A Long East-West Passage
newbee18626@newbee.description:
This is a long, narrow passage leading east and west.  The walls are
damp and covered with mildew and fungus.  There is a very unhealthy air
about this place and you're beginning to want out of here... soon.

newbee18642@newbee.title: The North Stairs
newbee18642@newbee.description:
Here, the hall opens into a wide room, with a high domed roof.  Now that
that you have come clear of the enclosed passage, you can see that the &+Gstair
leads upward to an open air balcony overlooking the area.  To the south the
room continues, and another stair is visible matching the one in front of
you.

newbee18640@newbee.title: The Statue's Room
newbee18640@newbee.description:
Here, the passage enters a small room.  Exits lead to the east and south,
and you notice a wonderful, large (and tastefully done) &+Cstatue&* to the north.

newbee18643@newbee.title: The Balcony
newbee18643@newbee.description:
Here you can look out and observe the world around.  Constructed in a
semi-circle around the dome of the room, the balcony allows you to look
out in almost any direction.  Wandering to the north end, you can see the
the valley to the north, and a village to the east.

newbee18647@newbee.title: The South Stairs
newbee18647@newbee.description:
Here, the hall opens into a wide room, with a high domed roof.  Now that
that you have come clear of the enclosed passage, you can see that the &+Gstair
leads upward to an open air balcony overlooking the area.  To the north the
room continues, and another &+Gstair&* is visible matching the one in front of
you.

newbee18602@newbee.title: The Dirty Hallway
newbee18602@newbee.description:
You continue wandering down the hallway.  Nothing much different here,
but you are positive you here noises behind the door to the south, and
coming from the east.  The walls are a bit slimy and moldy here... yeech,
couldn't they hire someone to clean this place?  What will the newbies
think?  Oh well, you can continue along the hallway to the east or west.

newbee18628@newbee.title: A Corner Room
newbee18628@newbee.description:
This room is hardly more than a crossing of passages.  You do sense a
slight breeze wafting down the passage to the north though, but it smells
altogether bad...

newbee18622@newbee.title: Another Corner
newbee18622@newbee.description:
The passage turns from north to west here.  The walls are still
covered with the same disgusting green fungus you have seen all
along, and you hear sounds of creatures moving all around you...

newbee18625@newbee.title: A Large Room
newbee18625@newbee.description:
The passage opens into a large oval room.  There really isn't much of
interest here though.

newbee18621@newbee.title: A T-Intersection In The Passage
newbee18621@newbee.description:
This is an intersection of a long east-west passage with a corridor
leading south.  The air seems a bit clearer here though, as if you were
approaching an exit.

newbee13@newbee.title: Heading Into Danger
newbee13@newbee.description:
Being the adventurous type, you march right into danger looking to battle
some monsters.  If you can clear this area of its monsters, you'll be ready
to go adventuring in the real world.  It all starts west of here.

   Hope you've done your strength training...

newbee18638@newbee.title: A Large Room
newbee18638@newbee.description:
You almost stumble as you enter this room... the sudden feeling of no
walls on either side of you makes you a bit nervous.  Suddenly you are
vulnerable on all sides.  You can't even tell how big a room this is,
because it extends to the east farther than you light will reach...

newbee18611@newbee.title: Another Corner
newbee18611@newbee.description:
Another corner of the passage, and just as untidy as the rest of
this place (maybe more so?).  There is a door to the east though...
wonder where that leads?  Oh, and the hallway continues west and
north.

newbee18610@newbee.title: A Brighter Hallway
newbee18610@newbee.description:
The hallway continues on in a east-west direction... and it seems to
be brightening up to the west.

newbee18607@newbee.title: More Of The Hallway
newbee18607@newbee.description:
Oh joy!  More of this annoying passage.  Perhaps there is something
more exciting through that door to the west?  Or you can keep searching
the hallways to the north or south.

newbee18624@newbee.title: Another Turn
newbee18624@newbee.description:
Hmmm... the passage turns south here.  You beginning to realize you
can easily lose your bearings if you aren't careful, and you don't think
you would like spending too much time here...

newbee18627@newbee.title: A Crossing Of Corridors
newbee18627@newbee.description:
Here a narrow east-west passage crosses with a wider passage to the
north and south.  The air is dank, and has an odor of decay and debris.
Not a nice place at all really...

newbee18612@newbee.title: The Alchemist's Room
newbee18612@newbee.description:
Lots of bottles and flasks lie about this room, but it all looks like
worthless clutter.  It appears whatever alchemist has been working here
is really very adept at his art.  There are a lot of formulae and spells
written on the walls too... couldn't he buy some paper?  There is a door
to the north, and also a dark &+Gstairway&* in the corner leading down, with a
large &+Gsign&* next to it that you probably should read...

newbee18636@newbee.title: A Branch To The South
newbee18636@newbee.description:
The east-west passage branches of to the south here.  All around you
is the odour of death.  Actually, the mold and fungus on the walls is
doing great, but otherwise... well... you don't want to think about what
else lives here.

newbee18645@newbee.title: The Balcony
newbee18645@newbee.description:
Here you can look out and observe the world around.  Constructed in a
semi-circle around the dome of the room, the balcony allows you to look out
in almost any direction.  Wandering to the south end, you can see the great
southern desert, and to the west, a vast mountain range.

mob18611@newbee.name: mob18611
mob18611@newbee.examine:
What a jerk!  He won't shut up, and he keeps making the most irritating
comments about everything.  Better silence him with cold, tempered steel
MUHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHA!
mob18611@newbee.description: A newbie is here annoying the hell out of you.

mob18604@newbee.name: mob18604
mob18604@newbee.examine:
The Guard also had the job of taking care of the Alchemist's pet dragon,
but he doesn't seem to be doing a good job of it.  He looks at you and
says, 'Have you seen that dragon?  Master will have my head if I don't find
him.'
mob18604@newbee.description: The Newbie Guard is here wondering where that dragon went.

mob18609@newbee.name: mob18609
mob18609@newbee.examine:
A massive man, with the head of a bull.  He looks as strong as bull too,
but not nearly as smart.  Actually, now that you consider it... he looks
a heck of a lot meaner than any bull you have ever seen... and he is
coming this way!
mob18609@newbee.description: The Great Minotaur is wondering just what you'll taste like.

mob18608_2@newbee.name: mob18608_2
mob18608_2@newbee.examine:
Little green, vaguely humoniod shaped creature, with a long pointed tail.
It is hard to say because before you ever get a good look at it, it darts
back into the shadows.
mob18608_2@newbee.description: A funny little imp-like thing (a quasit perhaps?) is sneaking about here.

mob18607_3@newbee.name: mob18607_3
mob18607_3@newbee.examine:
This guy has been lost in here too long... it is more zombie than man
now.  You would feel sorry for it, but it is moving in to attack!
mob18607_3@newbee.description: A VERY gaunt looking newbie... it looks like a zombie!

mob18605@newbee.name: mob18605
mob18605@newbee.examine:
He is a funny looking, furry little dude.  He looks really busy trying to
mix up a batch of something or other.
mob18605@newbee.description: The Newbie Alchemist is here trying to make something.

mob18606_2@newbee.name: mob18606_2
mob18606_2@newbee.examine:
Yuck!  If they'd ever clean this place maybe it wouldn't attract vermin
like this disgusting, little, six-legged, brown bug.
mob18606_2@newbee.description: A creepy little crawling thing is scuttling along the floor at your feet.

mob18601@newbee.name: mob18601
mob18601@newbee.examine:
Ick... what a disgusting creature!  It is black and green and slimy
and it is drooling everywhere... looks mean too.
mob18601@newbee.description: The big, ugly pit-beast is standing here sizing you up.

mob18608_1@newbee.name: mob18608_1
mob18608_1@newbee.examine:
Little green, vaguely humoniod shaped creature, with a long pointed tail.
It is hard to say because before you ever get a good look at it, it darts
back into the shadows.
mob18608_1@newbee.description: A funny little imp-like thing (a quasit perhaps?) is sneaking about here.

mob18606_1@newbee.name: mob18606_1
mob18606_1@newbee.examine:
Yuck!  If they'd ever clean this place maybe it wouldn't attract vermin
like this disgusting, little, six-legged, brown bug.
mob18606_1@newbee.description: A creepy little crawling thing is scuttling along the floor at your feet.

mob18610@newbee.name: mob18610
mob18610@newbee.examine:
The soul of a long since passed on adventurer... it lurks here waiting for
a chance to bring death to any who cross its path.
mob18610@newbee.description: The dark spectre is lurking in the shadows.

mob18612@newbee.name: mob18612
mob18612@newbee.examine:
What a moron!  Every question that is answered in the help files, he will
ask and he will probably ask 2 or 3 times too.  This guy just doesn't get
it, best put him out of his misery.
mob18612@newbee.description: A newbie is here looking terribly confused.

mob18606@newbee.name: mob18606
mob18606@newbee.examine:
Yuck!  If they'd ever clean this place maybe it wouldn't attract vermin
like this disgusting, little, six-legged, brown bug.
mob18606@newbee.description: A creepy little crawling thing is scuttling along the floor at your feet.

mob18608_3@newbee.name: mob18608_3
mob18608_3@newbee.examine:
Little green, vaguely humoniod shaped creature, with a long pointed tail.
It is hard to say because before you ever get a good look at it, it darts
back into the shadows.
mob18608_3@newbee.description: A funny little imp-like thing (a quasit perhaps?) is sneaking about here.

mob18603@newbee.name: mob18603
mob18603@newbee.examine:
Awwww... how cute!  A little baby dragon.  He's about 3 feet long and you
just want to cuddle him to death... no, you really want to kill him to tell
the truth.  But, remember, even a little dragon can be a big problem.
mob18603@newbee.description: Someone's little pet dragon has gotten loose, and is sniffing about here.

mob18614@newbee.name: mob18614
mob18614@newbee.examine:
Hmmm... looks like he has been around a while, but he wandered a little
too far from home this time.  Don't think he knows quite where he is,
maybe you should help him out?
mob18614@newbee.description: A newbie is here wandering about aimlessly.

mob18607_1@newbee.name: mob18607_1
mob18607_1@newbee.examine:
This guy has been lost in here too long... it is more zombie than man
now.  You would feel sorry for it, but it is moving in to attack!
mob18607_1@newbee.description: A VERY gaunt looking newbie... it looks like a zombie!

mob18607_2@newbee.name: mob18607_2
mob18607_2@newbee.examine:
This guy has been lost in here too long... it is more zombie than man
now.  You would feel sorry for it, but it is moving in to attack!
mob18607_2@newbee.description: A VERY gaunt looking newbie... it looks like a zombie!

mob18615@newbee.name: mob18615
mob18615@newbee.examine:
Here is a guy who has it all together.  Nice equipment too, must have read
the help files, Eh?
mob18615@newbee.description: A newbie is here, and he looks quite sure of himself.

mob18608@newbee.name: mob18608
mob18608@newbee.examine:
Little green, vaguely humoniod shaped creature, with a long pointed tail.
It is hard to say because before you ever get a good look at it, it darts
back into the shadows.
mob18608@newbee.description: A funny little imp-like thing (a quasit perhaps?) is sneaking about here.

mob18602@newbee.name: mob18602
mob18602@newbee.examine:
What an odd looking little beast.  He looks harmless, but you never can
tell.  He is only about 4 feet tall, but he pretty muscular looking...
maybe you should ask if he needs help?  Nah... kill him.
mob18602@newbee.description: The newbie monster stands here looking confused.  Kill him!  Kill him!

mob18602_1@newbee.name: mob18602_1
mob18602_1@newbee.examine:
What an odd looking little beast.  He looks harmless, but you never can
tell.  He is only about 4 feet tall, but hes pretty muscular looking...
maybe you should ask if he needs help?  Nah... kill him.
mob18602_1@newbee.description: The newbie monster stands here looking confused.  Kill him!  Kill him!

mob18616@newbee.name: mob18616
mob18616@newbee.examine:
In true kamikaze fashion, this newbie attacks anything that moves, in a
desperate bid for points.  Only problem is, hes always getting killed cause
he stupidly attacks Puff the Fractal Dragon every reset.
mob18616@newbee.description: A newbie in kamikaze-like fashion attacks everything...including YOU!

mob18613@newbee.name: mob18613
mob18613@newbee.examine:
Well, at least this gal seems pretty cool.  Talks a lot, but she's a
friendly, interesting sort.  Seems to have a clue what she's doing also,
unlike some others you might see.
mob18613@newbee.description: A newbie is here talking a lot.

mob18607@newbee.name: mob18607
mob18607@newbee.examine:
This guy has been lost in here too long... it is more zombie than man
now.  You would feel sorry for it, but it is moving in to attack!
mob18607@newbee.description: A VERY gaunt looking newbie... it looks like a zombie!
